channel.title: Gangstascape V4 [70% done] best and last release. with client
channel.description:
Hey guys... last release... getting pretty bored of RSPS, gonna move on in life.
Gangstascape v4 ~
Features:
TOP HAT FIXED DFS BANDOS KITESHIELD - 100% to SilentCJ
~~~7 QUESTS~~~ -Bananas -Dragon Slayer -Monkey Madness -Murder Mystery -Desert Treasure -Wizard of Mort'ton -Rune Mysteries
-MUSIC -SOUND EFFECTS -Level 1, 2, and 3 Treasure trails, 27 total clues. -Nearly full combat(Melee, range, magic) -ONLY SERVER SOURCE THAT HAS WORKING GRAND EXCHANGE (my pride and joy lol) -100% REAL Barrows mini game. -2 Random events -Ghostly Robes recieved from different Ghosts(after finishing Desert Treasure quest) -Working Dwarf Multi Cannon(Coolest version, cannon parts recieved from random event) -Nearly all skills trainable.(aglity,farming and thieving weren't added cause I got lazy.) -90% Special Attacks -Working Prayers(not all finished) -Working Potions. -Auto Skill cape trimming(2 99s or more) -Good Guthan and Dharok Armour Specials -Admins Arent Aloud to Trade -Working Make X (cooking, fletching, smithing) -Sorta Working Tztok-Jad(got messed up when I transfered the good version from my other server) -Trade Scamming Fixed -Fixed Magic on Npcs that have no combat level -Godsword Challenges -Rare Drops -Rare Items recieved from Genie Random Event, very very rare. -Most npcs drop 1-10k Coins so thats how you make money. -All npcs in the server so far have animations, except zombies and goblins...ugh. -Fixed 2handed weapons, you can't wield a shield item after you wield a 2h weapon
Pics(crappy but you get the point): [img]http://img519.imageshack.us/img519/554/screen7tp3.png[/img] - from bubly.
new edge look. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture1-2.gif[/img] summoning attacking. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture10-2.gif[/img] DBA spec. (75% spec bar) [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture11-1.gif[/img] SS spec... it has a delay on the sara gfx on the other person... so its pretty close to real rs one. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture12-1.gif[/img] Fight pits... i added but i haven't checked if it was working. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture13-1.gif[/img] quests [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture14-1.gif[/img] veng other (only last 10 seconds) [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture2-1.gif[/img] working prayer [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture3-1.gif[/img] made it so you can still hit through prayer, but not to much. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture4-1.gif[/img] summoning npcs: [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture9-1.gif[/img] deep wildy with dragons :o [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture7-1.gif[/img] VENG: sorry about the "trading center" i was at my G.E. [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture8-1.gif[/img] G.E. :D [IMG]http://i268.photobucket.com/albums/jj40/Gh0stJr/Picture6-1.gif[/img]
